A color management plugin for compiz 0.9.

Dependencies are only compiz and lcms.  The ICC profile is retrieved using the
_ICC_PROFILE atom as set by gnome-color-manager.  Compiz-style window
exclusions are supported.

This plugin is based on code from the compicc plugin by Kai-Uwe Bergmann:
http://compicc.sf.net/

To install:
$ sudo apt-get install compiz-dev liblcms1-dev
$ git clone https://github.com/gebner/compiz-cms.git
$ mkdir compiz-cms/build
$ cd compiz-cms/build
$ cmake ..
$ make install
And enable in CCSM.
